"You are welcome to come and tour the gym and meet our team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Du er altid velkommen til at kigge forbi klatrehallen og møde vores team."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You as well have goods to sell because some climbers may forget their chalk "
"or hurt their fingers... Let's see how the <strong>Point of Sale App "
"</strong>can help you quickly sell such products."
msgstr ""
"Du har også varer at sælge, for nogle klatrere har måske glemt deres "
"magnesium eller fået småskader på fingrene. Med <strong>POS-appen </strong> "
"kan du hurtigt og nemt sælge disse produkter."

#. module: climbing_gym
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:climbing_gym.welcome_article_body
